---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Our Story">

  <!-- ═══ HERO BANNER ═══ -->
  <section class="relative bg-stone-900 text-white py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-stone-900/80 to-stone-900/95"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
        The story behind the bakery that became a Glendale tradition.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ORIGIN STORY ═══ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
          It all started with a love of baking and a suitcase full of family recipes. Sam arrived in
          Glendale with a dream: to share the flavors of Armenia with a new community. He found a small
          storefront on Raleigh Street, fired up the ovens, and began baking the breads and pastries
          his family had perfected over generations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Word spread quickly. The aroma of fresh-baked gata, the perfect crunch of lahmajun, the soft
          pull of a warm choreg — neighbors, then their friends, then food lovers from all over Los
          Angeles began making the trip to that little bakery on Raleigh Street.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Today, Sam's Armenian Bakery remains a cornerstone of the Glendale community. The recipes
          have not changed. The ingredients are still the finest we can find. And every morning, the
          ovens light up to carry forward a tradition that means everything to us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TESTIMONIALS STRIP ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-16 lg:py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        {[
          {
            quote: "The gata at Sam's is unlike anything else in Glendale. Absolutely divine.",
            source: "Local Food Blog",
          },
          {
            quote: "A true neighborhood gem — authentic, consistent, and always made with care.",
            source: "Glendale Weekly",
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-6 lg:pl-8">
            <p class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl text-stone-800 italic leading-relaxed mb-3">
              "{item.quote}"
            </p>
            <cite class="not-italic text-sm tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-stone-400 font-medium">{item.source}</cite>
          </blockquote>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE SAM'S WAY ═══ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-0">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] lg:aspect-auto lg:h-[520px] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-100 via-orange-50 to-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary/30" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0022.5 18.75V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 3H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 21z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-400 text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">Baking Process Image</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 py-16 lg:py-0 lg:px-12 xl:px-20">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-5 leading-tight">The Sam's Way</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            At Sam's, every pastry is a labor of love. We believe in doing things the right way —
            giving dough time to rise, using real butter instead of shortcuts, and baking in small
            batches so nothing leaves our kitchen that is not exceptional.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Quality is not just a word here; it is the foundation of everything we do. From selecting
            the finest walnuts for our gata to milling our own spice blends for lahmajun, every detail
            matters.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            That is the Sam's way — and it is why our customers keep coming back.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ COMMUNITY ═══ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-0">
        <div class="px-6 py-16 lg:py-0 lg:px-12 xl:px-20 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-5 leading-tight">Part of the Community</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We have always been grateful for the warmth of the Glendale community. From our earliest
            days, neighbors welcomed us, shared our pastries with their families, and helped spread
            the word about what we do.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            We strive to give back in every way we can — supporting local events, donating to community
            organizations, and keeping our doors open as a gathering place where everyone feels at home.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] lg:aspect-auto lg:h-[520px] bg-gradient-to-bl from-rose-50 via-amber-50 to-orange-50 order-1 lg:order-2 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary/30" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0022.5 18.75V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 3H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 21z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-400 text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">Community Image</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ VISIT CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-stone-900 text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Come Visit Us</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We would love to welcome you to our bakery. Stop by for a fresh pastry, a warm loaf of bread,
        or simply to say hello.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-primary text-white text-sm tracking-[0.12em] uppercase font-medium hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors"
        >
          Get Directions
        </a>
        <a
          href="/menu"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 border border-white/30 text-white text-sm tracking-[0.12em] uppercase font-medium hover:border-white transition-colors"
        >
          View Our Menu
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
